{"tid":719434,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［認清事實］美斯領導能力真係唔得，做唔到球王都係呢點。","createTime":"2018-06-27T12:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T03:55:24.000Z","uid":43785,"like":27,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"29336d57e893c1def98367ec8a2f5af92270ca5c","tid":719434,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"美斯半場唔入更衣室，在外面搵記者影住訓話，<br />\n但半場後成隊表現仲差過上半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後，成場比賽交失好多次波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我支持既美斯係好波既，但係領導就真係差一班。<br />\n<br />\n反觀一個偉大領袖係令團隊發揮超水準。<br />\n美斯做，令團隊發揮唔到應有水準。<br />\n<br />\n換轉係發揮得好，尋晚點會入唔到三球以上？<br />\n<br />\n美斯領導能力真係唔得，做唔到球王都係因為呢點。我話你球王都受之有愧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申美斯球迷，唔想盲撐。"},{"pid":"06f5ab6e9ca2ef8ab263c2f0df3cfce613ac3e52","tid":719434,"uid":50744,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"巴打你走先 有我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefc8dce4151d5e75cb5d1054acb0647b0e0102b","tid":719434,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"06f5ab6e9ca2ef8ab263c2f0df3cfce613ac3e52","tid":719434,"uid":50744,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"巴打你走先 有我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcbff3e5fea74c45ad7c77e244c9db6514ff192","tid":719434,"uid":43785,"like":17,"dislike":9,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"06f5ab6e9ca2ef8ab263c2f0df3cfce613ac3e52","tid":719434,"uid":50744,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"巴打你走先 有我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"好老實，講真話既人有幾多？<br />\n一場波吹到上神領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係美斯迷都唔服啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁多年，咁多場，<br />\n美洲杯射唔入12碼，<br />\n呢係後面 垂頭喪氣，冇激勵隊友。<br />\n事後拉隊放棄足球，咁樣係真正好隊長表現咩？<br />\n對上兩場，踢到好似耶穌好似受難咁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得美斯係世上最頂尖既足球運動員，但絕對唔係足球場上偉大既領導者。"},{"pid":"b3c0028496a49a744be6363b0e22ef129d5df02e","tid":719434,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扲到世界杯我都係咁講<br />\n美斯唔係一個領袖才料"},{"pid":"6e83fc546ee97817ae0ac386d77bb1c562b37eba","tid":719434,"uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"你係撚美斯迷咩， 反得達哥就知你唔理性"},{"pid":"40af11d9c6d7144dfae6709c670f69dcf9ef0891","tid":719434,"uid":56589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"係咪唔比進步"},{"pid":"2dec9af4df130d6aace54b03fed6a8ac5c24dc1d","tid":719434,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"544eb4f6e04910b42634fed5dd4fab5bdc92a6d4","tid":719434,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcd43f34c29a2bf6c197d582a3ddc785b7c9dcc","tid":719434,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e83fc546ee97817ae0ac386d77bb1c562b37eba","tid":719434,"uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"你係撚美斯迷咩， 反得達哥就知你唔理性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-2